Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.99,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}MECHANICAL MARIE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:33.31,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}EPISODE 1:\NMARIE YANG PENUH KEBOHONGAN DAN RAHASIA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, maaf membuat Anda menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kami menyelesaikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pelayan robot, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia seperti manusia sungguhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak percaya kamu berhasil membuatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perusahaan nomor satu di negara ini\Nmemang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perusahaan yang kuwarisi\Nbisa melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku belum sepenuhnya yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kulihat lebih dekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ambil pemadam api!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jamnya meledak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sial, ini gawat!\N- Sial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bawakan pemadam api!\N- Ini lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Cepat!\N- Bawa semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan setelah menyaksikan ledakan itu,\Ndia masih tak terpengaruh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Petugas Kebersihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu yang menukar jam itu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku hanya disuruh melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jika ada yang mau kamu katakan,\N- Aku tak tahu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- jelaskan kepada kami!\N- ada mekanisme seperti itu di dalamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar, aku bersumpah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong ampuni aku, Tuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang mengawasiku dari atap rumah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Singkirkan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum itu, lepaskan penyadap\Nyang dipasang di bawah meja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Menyerahlah!\N- Lepaskan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada paket dan buket untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aroma mawarnya harum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia, demi keinginan mereka sendiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan menyakiti orang lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mencuri dari mereka,\Natau menjebak mereka tanpa ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku hanya memercayai benda anorganik\Nyang tak memiliki emosi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama pemuda ini Arthur Louis Zetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pewaris perusahaan besar,\Ntapi lahir di luar nikah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerabatnya yang membenci hal ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah berusaha menculik, meracuni,\Nserta membunuhnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi semuanya gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini membuatnya\Nsangat tak memercayai manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika kuberi tahu\Nmanusia macam apa yang paling kubenci?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia yang berbohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia yang membohongiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kugunakan semua kekuatanku\Nuntuk menghancurkan status sosial mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, robot pelayan ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seintens apa pun dia bergerak\Natau seganas apa pun serangan lawannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa mengusir musuh tanpa berkedip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Genius seni bela diri\Nyang dapat nama "Robot",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie Evans,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebenarnya hanya manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka melunasi utang orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu alasannya aku menerima pekerjaan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku tidak tahu soal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku bicara berdua\Ndengan pelayan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekejam apa pun penampilanku,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak akan bisa lolos dengan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan dibunuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh ada robot pelayan!\NIni hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini semacam plot novel ringan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat bersemangat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya akan membersihkan ruangannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bahkan terdengar\Nseperti gadis sungguhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu yang kamu sadari?\N- Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bolehkah aku memanggilmu Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah Tuan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini sungguh orang\Nyang sama seperti sebelumnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu seharusnya sudah menyadarinya kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu ada orang\Nyang mau membunuh Tuan Muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuatur agar kamu bisa ke sekolah.\NLindungi Tuan Muda di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mendengarkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena aku hanya bisa makan\Nsaat Tuan sedang mandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roti apitku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika mungkin, tolong siapkan\Nmakanan berprotein tinggi lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harus sangat berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia tahu kamu manusia,\Nkita berdua akan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terlambat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terlambat 0,089 detik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, saya terlambat bangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat menakutkan pagi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun yang tak bisa tepat waktu,\Ntak bisa dipercaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali berhati-hatilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, ucapannya cukup tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kelas,\Naku harus menghadiri kursus kuliah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuliah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ilmu Kenegaraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, aku akan makan malam\Ndengan para keturunan perusahaan mitra kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti sulit menjadi pewaris...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria itu tak punya\Nsopan santun di meja makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mungkin akan sangat marah\Nhingga menusuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, dia menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, dia sangat lembut padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya kamu akan pura-pura jadi manusia\Ndan pergi ke sekolah denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terjadi sesuatu, segera hubungi aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bingung sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa sangka aku bisa bersekolah\Ndi tempat sebagus ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Tuan memenangkan semua ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:56.00,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}RUANG OSIS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga anggota OSIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu hanya berdiri di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu wajah orang yang menyesal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti robot saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menakutkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua bilang begitu sejak aku kecil,\Njadi sudah terbiasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan ibuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak yang aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah aku memarahi atau memujinya,\Nekspresinya tak pernah berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa\Nmembesarkan anak sedingin ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan pelayanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Kamu di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang baru kamu katakan tentangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hanya lelucon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajahmu yang tanpa ekspresi itu cukup manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali pertama dalam hidupku
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada yang pernah mengatakan itu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tak bertemu, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tampak sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga tampak sehat, Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu nama kakak Tuan Muda,\NTuan Maynard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia juga mengincar nyawa Tuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kamu memenangkan\Nbeberapa kejuaraan di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harus istirahat, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga baru kembali dari belajar\Ndi luar negeri, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu hanya pertukaran dua pekan.\N- Ya, aku belajar cukup banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kenapa Ayah harus memilih\N- Kamu juga harus mengalaminya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- pria menjengkelkan ini?\N- Jika kamu terus tidak tidur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jika bukan karena kamu,\N- untuk belajar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- aku bisa saja mewarisi keluarga Zetes!\N- kamu tak akan menjadi penerus yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mungkin karena seleramu yang jelek.\N- Astaga, jangan menekanku, Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Siapa yang seleranya jelek?\N- Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Enyahlah, dasar perusak pemandangan!\N- Tidak biasanya kamu mengatakan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kamu yang harus menyerah.\N- Kakak,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mana mungkin aku menyerah, Berengsek!\N- kita harus selalu saling membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku sudah mengirim banyak pembunuh.\N- Kita bersaudara,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kenapa kamu tidak mati saja?\N- bukan begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Karena itu sangat jelas, Kakak.\N- Terima kasih, Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa setiap kali aku melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur dan Tuan Maynard\Nbertukar hinaan telepati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat dekat dengan kakaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama aku tak bicara denganmu,\Njadi aku agak gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau ke toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pembunuh yang kukirim gagal lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toiletnya di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan muncul tiba-tiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengagetkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak terlihat menyesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.54,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}MERASA SANGAT MENYESAL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, karena saya robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya pelayan robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bahkan tak tersentak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sungguh terlihat seperti robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memercayainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mempertahankan pelayan di sisinya\Nyang bahkan tak bisa tersenyum,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur tidak sehebat dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya juga bisa tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.57,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}DISENSOR SENDIRI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak hari itu, aku memutuskan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk menjadi penerus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan minum tehnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seram.\NSuasana hatinya lagi jelek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau meminta bantuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bolehkah aku berbaring di pangkuanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keras sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Produk logam memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, itu otot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sudah lama\Naku tak merasa setenang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak punya teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku memutuskan untuk hidup sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku orang istimewa yang dipilih ayahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tak ada yang memihakku,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku harus membuat diriku kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan bisa mengandalkan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan pun itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya selalu menemani Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saat bersamaku,\Ndia menunjukkan ekspresi anak seusianya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau melindunginya\Nseperti dia melindungiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau melindunginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membohongi orang ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:24.95,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}MECHANICAL MARIE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuliahnya dimulai pukul 17.00\Ndan selesai pukul 19.00, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mobil pikapnya tiba sedikit lebih awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih baik cepat daripada terlambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati di jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang untuk menjemput Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mobil itu palsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, cepat hubungi polisi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penampilan ini\Nsangat cocok untukmu, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat perilaku kasar\Npelayan robotmu yang dingin,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kesabaranku akhirnya mencapai batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali, pilih pelayanmu\Ndengan lebih bijak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kamu akan mati hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tak akan ada lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali ke-168 kamu mengatakan itu, Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, saya datang untuk menjemputmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada orang di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan orang, tapi robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku tak bisa melihat ke depan.\N- Singkirkan saja dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada kata-kata terakhir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ini soal keluarga Zetes,\Njangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan mewarisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya kamu melempar Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski dia robot, dilempar seperti itu,\Ndia akan hancur di udara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku turut berduka cita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun itu, jika mereka menghina Marie,\Naku tak akan memaafkannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seram.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya kamu akan menghantuiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu akan mengutukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kamu akan mati hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tak akan ada lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merekam semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan kamu merekamnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu alat pengawas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Metodemu kotor, dasar pengecut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Video ini sudah diunggah ke cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran apa yang akan terjadi\Njika itu diunggah di media sosial, Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.75,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}MAYNARD LOUIS ZETES
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.34,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SISI TERSEMBUNYI PEWARIS KAYA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu akan mati hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.88,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}LEBIH HINA DARI BINATANG
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tak akan ada lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru ingat sesuatu yang mendesak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya kalian saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kita lakukan padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah melihat wajah kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak bisa membiarkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kamu mau melakukannya, cepatlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kamu anak seorang selir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan lebih baik bagi semua orang\Njika kamu menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mengerti bahwa aku\Ntidak dibutuhkan oleh siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, meski waktu kita bersama\Ntidak lama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku senang bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang tak dibutuhkan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana mobilnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bukankah Tuan Maynard membawanya?\N- Kamu bercanda? Monster apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya senang Tuan selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga, Marie.\NAku senang kamu selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh, dia membuatku\Nmelalui banyak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kembali, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak baik berlama-lama di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangganya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangganya tak bisa dilalui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jongkok dan bernapaslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tutup wajahmu dengan saputangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada jalan keluar lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu satu-satunya jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, saya akan membantumu berdiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong keluar lewat jendela itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganmu, Marie?\NApa yang akan kamu lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena saya robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, aku tak bisa\Nmeninggalkanmu di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada cara lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan membiarkan Tuan mati di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa\Nmembuatnya meninggalkanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, sejujurnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memberi tahu semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaanku yang sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu yang saya habiskan bersamamu\Nsangat menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tak punya ekspresi dan emosi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya jarang merasa bahagia\Nsaat bersama orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, bagi saya, Tuan adalah\Norang yang sangat penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan bukan orang\Nyang bisa menghilang begitu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuh saya terbuat dari logam,\Njadi sangat kokoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong cari saya saat apinya padam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya pasti akan menyala ulang\Ndan terus melayani Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku pasti akan kembali\Nuntuk menyelamatkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku akan menyelamatkanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai akhir,\Naku masih berbohong padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya darah dan daging.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi Tuan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seluruh keberadaanku dipalsukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, perasaanku ini
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat tulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak menyala ulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kamu rusak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, aku menghubungi Roy\Ndan memintanya menyelamatkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu artinya\Nsaya bisa melayanimu lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, perkembangan ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kita akan terekspos?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, satu-satunya alasan aku melihat\NMarie tersenyum seperti gadis manusia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti karena aku kekurangan oksigen\Ndan membuatku berhalusinasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, berhentilah memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada gunanya
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jatuh cinta dengan mesin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meski dia manusia sungguhan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mustahil dia jatuh cinta\Ndengan orang sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur yang membenci manusia,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Marie yang berpura-pura menjadi robot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat melayani Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana kisah mereka akan terungkap?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.39,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}PRATINJAU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersiaplah, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Musuh Terbesarmu" akan muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:40.98,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}MECHANICAL MARIE\NEPISODE 2: MARIE DICURIGAI
